{"tid":1647964,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[土炮App] 狗車識別系統 v0.1","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:16:36.000Z","uid":312313,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d79f01bab01cc92c3a1f787a799b86bf83bfe6","tid":1647964,"uid":312313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次post, 有錯請用力指正<br />\n<br />\n為方便部份發夢人仕避免誤上狗車, 本公司膽粗粗用左一晚時間粗製濫造左個App幫大家一鍵檢查(非常不可靠)<br />\n<br />\nSource Code現以GPL License形式公開放喺GitLab上面, 有興趣嘅巴打可以自己上去望下, 400幾行Code仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/solarvolthk/carlookup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fsolarvolthk%2Fcarlookup&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=79441246\" target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/solarvolthk/carlookup</a><br />\n<br />\n由於唔識release嘅關係, 非正式版既Apk同埋要用到嘅Database另外放左喺:<br />\n<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/solarvolthk/cardb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fsolarvolthk%2Fcardb&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=9fd1b383\" target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/solarvolthk/cardb</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人可以用呢條Link Download晒兩個必要嘅File<br />\n<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/solarvolthk/cardb/-/archive/master/cardb-master.zip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fsolarvolthk%2Fcardb%2F-%2Farchive%2Fmaster%2Fcardb-master.zip&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=1aceea67\" target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/solarvolthk/cardb/-/archive/master/cardb-master.zip</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">個App冇Sign過, 請自行評估風險, 或自行Build from source</span><br />\n<br />\n先講吓個原理先<br />\n個App就好似Google Lens咁會開個Camera然後Search下畫面上有冇咩字(用左Google OCR), 如果覺得係車牌嘅話, 就會經你設定好嘅Database去搵下有冇呢個車牌嘅資料然後顯示<br />\n咁所以個App會要求Camera同File Access兩個Permission<br />\n至於個Database點來...可以問下老豆點樣搵車<br />\n<br />\n至於介面呢, 就得兩粒掣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrj6Mxx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frrj6Mxx.jpg&h=d9276831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左下角粒掣揀Database file, sample db可以喺上面條Link搵到<br />\n中間嗰粒掣不解釋<br />\n<br />\n示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deE6MxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdeE6MxD.jpg&h=36e4bdd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WWdrxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WWdrxD.jpg&h=366f6f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個App暫時只係認得傳統車牌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">FAQ:</span><br />\n<br />\nQ1: 有冇系統需求?<br />\nA1: Android 7.0或以上(理論上), 暫時只係喺Pixel 3上面測試過(哪有錢)<br />\n<br />\nQ2: Android唔俾我install<br />\nA2: 請自行google點安裝untrusted apk<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 好L多Bug喎<br />\nA3: 土炮嘢係咁上下<br />\n<br />\nQ4: 會唔會俾對家拎左來用?<br />\nA4: 對家已經有人面識別+監控燈柱, 邊得閒玩呢D玩具仔...就算真係咁, 手足既安危點都比財物重要<br />\n<br />\nQ5: 有冇iOS版?<br />\nA5: iDog行開啦<br />\n<br />\nQ6: 個database點加新資料?<br />\nA6: 可以睇返GitLab上面嘅README<br />\n<br />\nQ7: Android 6.0以下有冇得用?<br />\nA7: 我建議你用警棍大大力打爆個mon然後踓落坑渠<br />\n<br />\n最後:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"2ba8aad8b899704a50e537e01fad5cd440cf7dd6","tid":1647964,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［核彈行動］令警察家變！針對警妻開闢新文宣線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9e6e0510f6392236f88d66ca0e2c64a288e9215","tid":1647964,"uid":328061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:57:20.000Z","msg":"喂 ! 個 <span style=\"color: orange;\">idea</span> 好正喎<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(iDog 行開啦)</span></span>，你呢句說話我十分喜歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77251ebbf9d58e96ba94dbeb99beb7ae95312b9c","tid":1647964,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:15:48.000Z","msg":"希望多d人比料更新，個app好有用"},{"pid":"bf7bd1b2ccac89f2909272b993f6eecb54dacd30","tid":1647964,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:47:47.000Z","msg":"Unmarked 嘅車牌係假㗎，車尾箱隨時有幾對替換<br />\n<br />\n如果靠認車牌就得，隱形戰車就收得工啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e008f0acfbafc2ee0f79f20aac3e3e2777d44c4e","tid":1647964,"uid":331229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}